"TC-SRCH-0001","Find Patient Record / Search","Search by Name","Search patient by full given and family name returns matching record","Functional","Smoke","P1","Critical","High","Logged in as Clinician at a session location; at least one patient ""John Tester"" exists; on the Find Patient Record screen","1. Open Find Patient Record | 2. Type the full name in the search box | 3. Wait for results to render | 4. Inspect the results table","Query=John Tester; Existing patient: Given=John, Family=Tester","Results table shows the patient ""Tester, John"" with Identifier, Gender, Age and Birthdate columns; the matching row is selectable","Automatable","REQ-SRCH-001","Patient Safety; PHI/Privacy","OpenMRS"
