"TC-SRCH-0028","Find Patient Record / Search","Pagination","Infinite scroll / load-more appends additional results","Functional","Regression","P3","Low","Low","Logged in as Clinician; >1 page of results; on Find Patient Record screen using scroll-based loading","1. Search for the shared family name | 2. Scroll to bottom of results | 3. Observe additional rows appended","Query=Common; pageSize=10","Scrolling triggers loading of the next batch; rows append without losing earlier rows or scroll position jumping","Partially-Automatable","REQ-SRCH-012","Usability","OpenMRS"
