"TC-SRCH-0031","Find Patient Record / Search","Open Record","Selecting a result row opens the patient dashboard","Functional","Smoke","P1","Critical","High","Logged in as Clinician; patient ""John Tester"" exists; on Find Patient Record screen","1. Search for the patient | 2. Click the matching result row | 3. Wait for navigation","Query=John Tester","Patient dashboard opens showing the correct patient's name, identifier, age and active visit context","Automatable","REQ-SRCH-014","Patient Safety; PHI/Privacy","OpenMRS"
"TC-SRCH-0032","Find Patient Record / Search","Open Record","Keyboard Enter on a focused result row opens the record","Accessibility","Regression","P2","Medium","Medium","Logged in as Clinician; patient ""John Tester"" exists; on Find Patient Record screen","1. Search for the patient | 2. Use Tab/arrow keys to focus the result row | 3. Press Enter","Query=John Tester","Focused result row activates on Enter and opens the correct patient dashboard","Partially-Automatable","REQ-SRCH-014","Accessibility; Patient Safety","OpenMRS"
"TC-SRCH-0033","Find Patient Record / Search","State Transition","Search box clears and resets results when input is emptied","State Transition","Regression","P3","Low","Low","Logged in as Clinician; a prior search returned results; on Find Patient Record screen","1. Perform a search returning results | 2. Clear the search box | 3. Observe results region","Query=John then empty","Results clear and the screen returns to its idle/recent state with no stale rows","Automatable","REQ-SRCH-015","Usability; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
