"TC-SRCH-0040","Find Patient Record / Search","Boundary","Very long query string is handled without crashing","Boundary","Regression","P3","Medium","Medium","Logged in as Clinician; on Find Patient Record screen","1. Open Find Patient Record | 2. Paste a 300-character string | 3. Submit | 4. Observe behavior","Query=300-char ""aaaa...""","Application truncates or processes gracefully, returns empty state, and does not throw a server error","Partially-Automatable","REQ-SRCH-008","Usability; Security","OpenMRS"
"TC-SRCH-0041","Find Patient Record / Search","Exploratory","Explore behavior when switching between name and ID mid-typing","Exploratory","Regression","P3","Low","Low","Logged in as Clinician; on Find Patient Record screen","1. Begin typing a name | 2. Delete and switch to typing an identifier | 3. Observe transitions and any flicker or stale state","Mixed: ""Joh"" then ""1001""","Search adapts to the new input class without stale results, duplicate rows, or UI errors; document any anomalies","Manual-Only","REQ-SRCH-015","Usability; Data Integrity","OpenMRS"
