"TC-SRCH-0046","Find Patient Record / Search","API","REST patient search by name returns expected JSON structure","API","Integration","P1","High","High","Valid session token; OpenMRS REST API reachable","1. Send GET to the patient search endpoint with name query | 2. Inspect HTTP status and JSON body","GET /ws/rest/v1/patient?q=Tester","HTTP 200 with a results array; each entry contains uuid, display, and identifiers; matching patient present","Automatable","REQ-SRCH-019","Standards-FHIR; PHI/Privacy","OpenMRS"
