"TC-SRCH-0048","Find Patient Record / Search","API","REST search with missing query parameter returns a clear error","API","Integration","P3","Low","Low","Valid session token; API reachable","1. Call the patient search endpoint without the q parameter | 2. Observe response","GET /ws/rest/v1/patient (no q)","Server returns a 400-class error with a descriptive message rather than an unbounded dump of all patients","Automatable","REQ-SRCH-019","Security; PHI/Privacy","OpenMRS"
