"TC-SRCH-0053","Find Patient Record / Search","HL7","Inbound HL7v2 QBP^Q22 patient query returns RSP with matching PID","HL7","Integration","P2","Medium","Medium","HL7 interface engine connected to a SMART/HAPI-backed registry; QBP profile supported","1. Send a QBP^Q22 query with patient name | 2. Capture the RSP^K22 response | 3. Parse PID segments","QBP^Q22; QPD name=Tester^John","RSP^K22 returns matching PID segment(s) with patient identifier and name; QAK acknowledges success","Manual-Only","REQ-SRCH-021","Standards-HL7; PHI/Privacy","Standards"
